      "tolerance_reason": "Bloomberg SWPM screen NPV is 155,363.65; finstack previously reconciled within 0.15% using the explicit compounded-SOFR underlier. The 2026-06 moderate-fix pass moved the option-expiry time axis to ACT/365F (calendar-time vol convention, matching the IR-future option pricer), leaving a documented ~0.83% residual on this 5Y-expiry OTM receiver. abs-or-rel: absolute/display tolerance is the intended comparison gate; relative tolerance is retained only as a legacy diagnostic."
    },
