      "tolerance_reason": "Finstack DV01 is a signed combined-curve bump measure and is not asserted as like-for-like Bloomberg screen DV01; Bloomberg's +2,250.50 value is retained in bloomberg_reference.finstack_reconciliation. abs-or-rel: absolute/display tolerance is the intended comparison gate; relative tolerance is retained only as a legacy diagnostic."
